[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2384_152900_000006_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2384/152900/2384_152900_000006_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2384",
        "content": "We also had quantities of loose straps.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2384_152900_000007_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2384/152900/2384_152900_000007_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2384",
        "content": "One man was sufficient to set up the tent in the stiffest breeze; I have come to the conclusion that the fewer poles a tent has, the easier it is to set up, which seems quite natural.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2384_152900_000007_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2384/152900/2384_152900_000007_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2384",
        "content": "There was no question of this with our tents.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2384_152900_000010_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2384/152900/2384_152900_000010_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2384",
        "content": "First the reindeer skins had to be bought in a raw state, and this was done for me by mr Zappfe at Tromsoe, Karasjok, and Kaatokeino.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2384_152900_000010_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2384/152900/2384_152900_000010_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2384",
        "content": "We then went to work to make clothes after the pattern of the Netchelli Eskimo, and the sewing went on early and late -- thick anoraks and thin ones, heavy breeches and light, winter stockings and summer stockings.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2384_152900_000010_000016",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2384/152900/2384_152900_000010_000016.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2384",
        "content": "It was easy to tie the end of the cover together like the mouth of the sack, and this kept the snow out of the bag during the day's march.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2384_152900_000010_000018",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2384/152900/2384_152900_000010_000018.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2384",
        "content": "We attached great importance to having the bags made of the very best sort of skin, and took care that the thin skin of the belly was removed.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2384_152900_000011_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2384/152900/2384_152900_000011_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2384",
        "content": "It is extraordinarily light and strong, and keeps the wind completely out.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2384_152900_000011_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2384/152900/2384_152900_000011_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2384",
        "content": "The others consisted of trousers and jacket with hood.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2384_152900_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2384/152900/2384_152900_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2384",
        "content": "Now, it is a fact that if one can wear soft foot gear exclusively the risk of frost bite is far less than if one is compelled to wear stiff boots; in soft foot gear, of course, the foot can move far more easily and keep warm.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2384_152900_000014_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2384/152900/2384_152900_000014_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2384",
        "content": "I want the ski to be a part of oneself, so that one always has full command of them.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2384_152900_000014_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2384/152900/2384_152900_000014_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2384",
        "content": "The sole was to be thick and stiff -- for we had to be prepared to use crampons -- but the uppers as soft as possible.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2384_152900_000016_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2384/152900/2384_152900_000016_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2384",
        "content": "This all came complete from a firm in Stockholm.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2384_152900_000016_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2384/152900/2384_152900_000016_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2384",
        "content": "There is never any trouble with this apparatus; it has come as near perfection as possible.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2384_152900_000017_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2384/152900/2384_152900_000017_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2384",
        "content": "There could be no better recommendation than this.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2384_152900_000019_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2384/152900/2384_152900_000019_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2384",
        "content": "The method is both simple and reliable.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2384_152900_000020_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2384/152900/2384_152900_000020_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2384",
        "content": "There is not a speck of rust on needles, scissors, knives, or anything else, although they have been exposed to much damp.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2384_152900_000020_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2384/152900/2384_152900_000020_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2384",
        "content": "Our own medical outfit, which was bought in Christiania, and according to the vendor's statement unusually well packed, became in a short time so damaged that the whole of it is now entirely spoilt.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2384_152900_000021_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2384/152900/2384_152900_000021_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2384",
        "content": "I have already spoken of the pemmican.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2384_152900_000021_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2384/152900/2384_152900_000021_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2384",
        "content": "Besides the pemmican, we had biscuits, milk powder, and chocolate.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2384_152900_000021_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2384/152900/2384_152900_000021_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2384",
        "content": "They were specially baked for us, and were made of oatmeal with the addition of dried milk and a little sugar; they were extremely nourishing and pleasant to the taste.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2384_152900_000021_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2384/152900/2384_152900_000021_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2384",
        "content": "These biscuits formed a great part of our daily diet, and undoubtedly contributed in no small degree to the successful result.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2384_152900_000021_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2384/152900/2384_152900_000021_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2384",
        "content": "Milk powder is a comparatively new commodity with us, but it deserves to be better known.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2384_152900_000021_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2384/152900/2384_152900_000021_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2384",
        "content": "It came from the district of Jaederen.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2384_152900_000021_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2384/152900/2384_152900_000021_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2384",
        "content": "We also took dried milk from a firm in Wisconsin; this milk had an addition of malt and sugar, and was, in my opinion, excellent; it also kept good the whole time.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
